<emphasis id="6FB0D079FF91EF52FF42FACAFEE7FA21" bold="true" box="[199,338,1407,1433]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Comments:</emphasis>
Field observations suggest that this is the less frequent species among those we recorded in the subfamily, since they were rarely found. Individuals extraordinarily camouflage themselves on tree trunks.
</paragraph>
